# Fashion E-commerce Website

## Overview

This is a responsive fashion e-commerce website designed for selling clothing, shoes, handbags, and fashion accessories. The website provides a clean shopping experience with an easy-to-use interface across desktop, tablet, and mobile devices.

## Features

- Responsive design
- Modern home page
- Product listing
- Product details
- Shopping cart
- Search functionality
- Category filtering
- User-friendly navigation
- Mobile-friendly layout

## Product Categories

- Clothing
- Shoes
- Handbags
- Fashion Accessories

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Bootstrap
- JavaScript

